	</tr>
	<tr>
		
			<td colspan="2" bgcolor="#DEDACB" background="http://www.everlore.com/gimages/tb_beige.gif">
		
				<font face="verdana" size="2" color="black">
				Yes, snare + panic animal is a very good combo, especially if you are teaming with fighters. Just keep on panicing the animal while the fighters wack away does wonders. But careful if ye try this on the griffawns. They tend to get an increase in AC when yer tryin to smack the back sides of them? I've grouped with two 15th lvl fighters and myself 14th and I paniced a blue fawn for my whole bar of mana (10 mana / spell for the entire mana bar, about 300?) and we finally managed to take the beasty down. Makes ya wonder. <BR>
<BR>
Roamer...
				</font>
			</td>

	</tr>
	
