				<font face="verdana" size="2" color="black">
				Don't know if anyone has tried this,but it's a little trick i like to do.When I was in west Karan and was lower Level this helped alot.Cast snare on a Lion,and as soon as you can Panic animal.The loin turns to run but is so slow you just beat on it  till it dies.Works best with one other person as you can kill before the snare or panic wear off,and if your buddy can get the attention of the lion it is easier to cast the spells on it.
				</font>
