				<font face="verdana" size="2" color="black">
				  Snare is a spell you should always have ready. Also in a group this can save someones life if the MOB is weak it loses it's ability to move at all. In a <BR>
close fight that means the weak guy who is trying to back off can take a break without getting his butt whuphed.  When I play with my rogue I wish other Druids would try to remember this.  I could have been saved the last 2 times I died, once when a almost dead Aviac Harrier decided that the 5 other party members<BR>
were not good fare and I was fairly far out trying to Bind wounds. It took that Harrier aobut 8 secs to get to me and I had to listen to all the apologizes afterward.<BR>

				</font>
